OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy in the evening with some patchy
OL,7,Flight rain, mainly in the west.
OL,8,FStaying mostly cloudy overnight with
OL,9,Ffurther spots of light rain at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FCloudy through the day,
OL,12,Fwarmer with the best chance of bright
OL,13,For sunny spells in the east. Outbreaks
OL,14,Fof rain the morning, these becoming
OL,15,Fconfined to the west by afternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA
OL,18,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,19,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
